<!-- WHY THIS MATTERS --><div style="margin-top:12px;background:#fbfdff;border:1px solid #dbe6f3;border-left:5px solid #009ef5;border-radius:14px;padding:14px 16px;color:#0e1e3d;">
<div style="font-weight:950;color:#1c2430;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:6px;">Why this matters</div>
<div style="color:#5b6b88;line-height:1.65;font-size:14px;">Defining information standards and production methods ensures information is consistent, verifiable, and usable beyond handover — reducing ambiguity, rework, and operational risk.</div>
